      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. The ride is super smooth, the interior is nice and clean, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next big adventure. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
