    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six independent throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including VANOS timing adjustment and rear subframe reinforcement to handle torsional stress. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics with refreshed bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and mid-corner stability. Mechanically robust and driver-focused, it represents a well-sorted chassis for the discerning enthusiast.",
